The paper is about Malicious URL Detection using Machine Learning, which falls under the category of Computer Security (cs.CR). The proposed approach uses deep learning techniques such as Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and word embeddings, which are commonly used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) research. The paper also involves Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques such as Bag-of-words and word embeddings, which are relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper uses image processing techniques such as CNNs to process the characters in the URL, which is related to Computer Vision (cs.CV).
